subject: College Athletics
lead_paragraph: EAST LANSING, Mich., Nov. 3 (AP) — Chad Henne’s 31-yard touchdown pass to Mario Manningham with 2 minutes 28 seconds left Saturday lifted 15th-ranked Michigan to a 28-24 victory over Michigan State in the teams’ 100th matchup.
